6.1 UMOJA-ai: Technology & Content Partner}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs22\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs22\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af8\langfe2052\sl-276\slmult0\ql\sb0\sa120{\rtlch\af8\afs22 \ltrch\loch\cf18\fs22\dbch\af8\loch
UMOJA-ai is responsible for all technology development, AI model training, curriculum content creation, hardware specification and procurement, teacher training programs, system maintenance and support, examination design and administration, and student registration infrastructure. UMOJA-ai retains intellectual property over the platform and operates as the central coordinating entity.}
